string.name: STR_WORLD_EVENT_WINTER_XP_BOOST_50_DESC
string.body: Grants you 50%% additional EXP from gathering, crafting, or hunting.\nThe effect expires after 30 minutes and there is a 30 minute cooldown before you can use it again.\nAffects all party members.

string.name: STR_WORLD_EVENT_WINTER_GATHER_BOOST_200_DESC
string.body: Increases acquisition of gathering, extraction, and Aether extraction skills.\nExpires after 30 minutes, and there is a 30 minute cooldown before you can use it again.\nAffects all party members.

string.name: STR_WORLD_EVENT_WINTER_AP_BOOST_30_DESC
string.body: Grants you 30%% additional Abyss Points. However, this item doesn't apply to rewards received from the Dredgion or the Empyrean Crucible.\nExpires after 30 minutes, and there is a 30 minute cooldown before you can use it again.\nAffects all party members.

string.name: STR_WORLD_EVENT_WINTER_CRAFT_BOOST_200_DESC
string.body: Increases acquisition of crafting and furniture crafting skills by 200%%.\nExpires after 30 minutes and there is a 30 minute cooldown before you can use it again.\nAffects all party members.

string.name: STR_WORLD_EVENT_WINTER_DROP_BOOST_20_DESC
string.body: Increases your item drop rate by 20%% when hunting.\nExpires after 30 minutes and there is a 30 minute cooldown before you can use it again.\nAffects all party members.

string.name: STR_LOGIN_MATTER_PROC_STUN_U1_65A_DESC
string.body: Imbues a weapon with a 7%% chance to stun a target for 1 second. There is a chance that the godstone will be destroyed when the effect is triggered.\nDouble-click to activate, and then select an item to socket.

string.name: STR_LOGIN_MATTER_PROC_PARALYZE_U1_65A_DESC
string.body: Imbues a weapon with an effect where there is a 3%% chance to paralyze a target for 4 seconds. There is a chance that the godstone will be destroyed when the effect is triggered.\nDouble-click to activate, and then select an item to socket.

string.name: STR_LOGIN_MATTER_PROC_ROOT_U1_65A_DESC
string.body: Imbues a weapon with an effect where there is a 3%% chance to immobilize a target for 10 seconds. There is a chance that the godstone will be destroyed when the effect is triggered.\nDouble-click to activate, and then select an item to socket.

string.name: STR_LOGIN_MATTER_PROC_SILENCE_U1_65A_DESC

string.name: STR_SPECIAL_KISK_LIGHT_PRIVATE_SMALL_DESC
string.body: Summons a Kisk that allows you to resurrect at the site it is installed at. It lasts for 2 hours and can be reinstalled after a cooldown time of 30 minutes.\nUp to 1 person can register and it may only be used by the summoner.

string.name: STR_SPECIAL_KISK_LIGHT_PARTY_SMALL_DESC
string.body: Summons a Kisk where you can resurrect from. It lasts for 2 hours and allows the registration of up to 6 people.\nOnly the members of the summoner's group can use it.

string.name: STR_SPECIAL_KISK_LIGHT_FORCE_MEDIUM_DESC
string.body: Summons a Kisk where you can resurrect from. It lasts for 2 hours and allows the registration of up to 24 people.\nIt can only be used by the members of the summoner's Force.

string.name: STR_STIGMA_N_FI_BURSERKLANCE_G1_DESC
string.body:
You must place this stone in a Greater Stigma slot.
When equipped in a Stigma slot, it allows you to use the Sure Strike skill.
It can be charged with the help of a Stigma Master.
When charging, an additional Stigma of the same type is required.

It can be charged with the help of a Stigma Master.
When charging, an additional Stigma of the same type is required.

string.name: STR_MATTER_ENCHANT_EXCEED_CRITICAL_01_DESC
string.body:
Enhances the basic attributes of an item.
Can be used for both regular and amplification enhancements.
When used for regular enhancements, critical enhancement occurs when successful.
Double-click to activate and select an item to enhance.

string.name: STR_EVENT_MATTER_ENCHANT_EXCEED_01
string.body: [Event] Enchantment Stone of the Empyrean Lord

string.name: STR_EVENT_MATTER_ENCHANT_EXCEED_01_7DAY_DESC
string.body:
It enhances the basic attributes of equipment including weapons and armor.
Can be used for both regular and amplification enhancements.
When used for regular enhancements, 1 level is reduced if the enhancement fails. For armor enhancements, additional chance is added for critical hits.
Activate the Enchantment Stone item by double-clicking (or right-clicking) it and select an item to enhance.
Can be used for 7 days.

string.name: STR_WORLD_EVENT_MATRYOSHKA_XP_BOOST_50_DESC
string.body: The Youngest Matryoshka's Amulet, which grants you 50%% additional EXP from gathering, crafting, or hunting creatures. \nThe effect expires after 30 minutes and there is a 30 minute cooldown before you can use it again.\nWhen used, it affects every member in your party.

string.body: This effect increases your acquisition of gathering, extraction, and Aether extraction skills by 200%%. \nThis effect expires after 30 minutes, and there is a 30 minute cooldown before you can use it again.\nWhen used, it affects every member in your party.

string.name: STR_WORLD_EVENT_MATRYOSHKA_AP_BOOST_30_DESC
string.body: This effect grants you 30%% additional Abyss Points. However, this item doesn't apply to rewards received from the Dredgion or the Tempere Training Camp.\nThe effect expires after 30 minutes, and there is a 30 minute cooldown before you can use it again.\nWhen used, it affects every member in your party.

string.name: STR_WORLD_EVENT_MATRYOSHKA_CRAFT_BOOST_200_DESC
string.body: This effect increases your acquisition of crafting and furniture crafting skills by 200%%.\nThe effect expires after 30 minutes and there is a 30 minute cooldown before you can use it again.\nWhen used, it affects every member in the group.

string.name: STR_WORLD_EVENT_MATRYOSHKA_DROP_BOOST_20_DESC
string.body: This effect increases your item drop rate by 20%% when hunting creatures.\nThe effect expires after 30 minutes and there is a 30 minute cooldown before you can use it again.\nWhen used, it affects every member in your party.
